{
  "stem": "9156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The place was torn up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Nazis had already come in and torn up things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the kid wanted to go to school, and perhaps eight years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the mother said, 'Be careful when you go to school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Don't say anything.' And he-- don't say anything when they spit on you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, 'I spit back.' And the mother says, 'If you spit back, your father will be killed.' I have always used that in my classes as an example how one can destroy courage in children.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it's understandable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You understand the mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know what's happening to that child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But that I saw with my own eyes, and I lived through it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was with these people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was sure that it would be the end anyhow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When a letter arrived from England, because that's where my sister was, and England wasn't as suspicious to be as from France.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we had a way of writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We knew how to write a code.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she gave me exactly when I should leave by train to Innsbruck, and that in Innsbruck would be somebody who would wear white gloves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I was supposed to wear white gloves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she would help me that I get into France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gee, I don't know whether I'd even still know it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You will think I pretend, but I don't remember it very well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had something to do with letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That we knew certain words started, but I can't tell it you for sure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had worked that out before we got-- knew we-- that we would get into prisons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this came partially from my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew it came also from Paul, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
